<quickviewtext name="Quick View">
<![CDATA[
<p>Could there be a more romantic major than wine? Students of the Viticulture (grape growing) &amp; Enology (wine making) major swish mouthfuls of Merlot and compare them to notes of coffee, lavender, wormwood, and star anise for a grade. They can crush grapes, ferment wine, and travel to France for internships. Come study grape growing and winemaking!</p>
]]>
